      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make an excellent, reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes mechanical function over cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its history with several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some minor fading on the hood. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays moderate wear on the upholstery and floor mats. Mechanically, it starts reliably and drives well, though it may eventually benefit from routine maintenance items like new brake pads or tires in the coming year. It's a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
