    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of a well-loved daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint still holds a deep, mirror-like gloss, though under direct sunlight, you may notice some minor road peppering on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the fuel door. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no significant curb rash, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a quiet, comfortable sanctuary. The premium upholstery is free of tears or stains, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster. All electronic components\u2014including the infotainment system, backup camera, and heated seats\u2014operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a fresh oil change and air filter replacement performed just last month. This car drives straight, brakes firmly, and offers a tight, responsive feel on the road. It comes with two sets of keys and a complete folder of maintenance records.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both reliability and a refined presence. It exhibits a well-documented history of maintenance, ensuring that its mechanical components operate with precision. The exterior retains a commendable finish, while the cabin offers a clean, sophisticated environment. Fully inspected and prepared for immediate delivery, this automobile represents a superior balance of performance and long-term value.",
